user_prompt: A developer, just 20 minutes away from the end of the workday, has discovered a bug. Frustrated, they are holding their head in their hands while reviewing the code, drained of energy, and typing away on the keyboard with a sense of desperation. Create a haptic stimulus that represents this scene.
prompt_variant: With just 20 minutes left in the day, the developer looks defeated while scrutinizing the code for bugs, feeling exhausted and stressed.
